---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="MOVA Kids | Future-Friendly Pediatric Dentistry" description="A calm, playful and technology-assisted dental experience designed around children and parents.">
<section class="kids-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">MOVA KIDS</span>
    <h1>A brave first step into lifelong oral health.</h1>
    <p class="lead">A future clinic concept combining preventive pediatric dentistry, emotional safety, playful education and parent guidance.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container grid grid-3">
    <article class="card"><h3>Fear-aware care</h3><p class="muted">Slow introductions, stop signals and age-appropriate language.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Prevention first</h3><p class="muted">Fluoride, fissure sealants and personalized hygiene coaching.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Bravery journey</h3><p class="muted">Digital certificates and positive milestones for every child.</p></article>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="container" style="padding:18px 0 42px"><small>ترجمه کامل این صفحه در مرحله بعد تکمیل می‌شود.</small></div>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
.kids-hero{padding:150px 0 100px;background:radial-gradient(circle at 70% 20%,#d9f3ff,transparent 30%),linear-gradient(135deg,#f7fbfd,#f3e9ff)}
.kids-hero h1{max-width:900px}
</style>
